# Solar Panel Cleaning System

An automated solar panel cleaning system designed for efficient maintenance using sensors for navigation and a water-efficient cleaning mechanism.

## Features
- Efficient cleaning of solar panels
- Navigation and obstacle detection using sensors
- Water-efficient cleaning mechanism

## Hardware Requirements
- Microcontroller (e.g., Arduino, Raspberry Pi)
- Ultrasonic or infrared sensors for obstacle detection
- Motors and wheels for movement
- Water reservoir and cleaning mechanism
- Power supply (batteries or power adapter)

## Software Requirements
- Arduino IDE or other relevant software for programming the microcontroller
- Necessary libraries for sensor integration
